{
  "stem": "25651.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mengele is a small item in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You all make up a big item out of it, because he is called the Angel of Death and all this business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was nothing of the sort.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a, a normal SS officer who did his job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what he would have said if there had ever been a trial.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have never seen him hit anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every time that I know something critical had to be done and when he was asked, he-- his response was fairly favorable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he was part of a machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The machine was the thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a terrible place, what-- the way that it was done.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was the ranks of the SS that were beating us and that were these-- this sort of regime of fear.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The officers stood aloof from that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were directing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, they were guilty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they didn't sully their hands, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a different order of bestiality, if you-- if you'd like to call it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mengele was just one of many.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, there was a whole system going there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you-- so your emphasis on Mengele is, is, to me--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I was out of his reach, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- except for this painting, which got burned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I was running along with this fire extinguisher, spraying people who were running behind me without knowing that it went off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this-- And I sprayed this SS man with this fire extinguishing stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he started shouting, sabotage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, that I did it purposely.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I am to report to him next day and this and that and the other.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
